rows.label: qst610506_msg0001
rows.name:
I see Invidian mercenaries
and Drivers on the move.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0002
rows.name:
Ah, come off it, lady. I
asked for you to keep a
lookout, not to prank me.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0003
rows.name:
I only want to hear things you actually
saw, got that? I mean, sure, the Invidian
army's stationed over thataway, but...

rows.label: qst610506_msg0004
rows.name:
You think I'm making things
up? I'm only telling you what
I saw with my own eyes.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0005
rows.name:
I'm not talking about the army,
either. They seem to be a group
called the Wildschwein Mercenaries.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0006
rows.name:
About twenty men or
so, moving covertly.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0007
rows.name: You can really tell all that?

rows.label: qst610506_msg0008
rows.name:
Blades can tell more than
you know, little boy...

rows.label: qst610506_msg0010
rows.name:
If you're telling the truth,
I might have to admit defeat
in our little contest...

rows.label: qst610506_msg0011
rows.name:
Are you sure this is the time
to be getting all mopey?

rows.label: qst610506_msg0012
rows.name:
Those mercs are very nearly
on top of us, you know.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0013
rows.name: Well, why didn't you say so sooner?!

rows.label: qst610506_msg0014
rows.name: I did say they were moving covertly...

rows.label: qst107604_msg0218
rows.name: インヴィディア人のドライバーが巨神獣兵器の下に来ている様子を映す

rows.label: qst610506_msg0015
rows.name: I'll back you up from here.

rows.label: qst610506_msg0016
rows.name:
You lot head down to the Divine Beast
weapon over yonder, taking out any
Invidians that get in your way!
